        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Crying doesn't make me any less of a man. To not show emotion, you're an idiot, or you're living a pipe dream. If someone were to tell me not to show emotion, I'd hit them in the lip.''</p>
        <p>LT. COL. MORRIS GOINS, reflecting on soldiers' reactions to losing comrades in Iraq. [A10]</p>
      </block>
